{"tid":567334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婚禮只顧特寫伴娘胸臀　英夫婦怒告攝影師","createTime":"2018-02-20T18:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T03:38:51.000Z","uid":42629,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5da8763826b570c3bc757e9484cea8720e907d49","tid":567334,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:33:01.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒周二（20日）報道，柴郡一對夫婦於2015年舉行婚禮，聘請了一名男攝影師拍下婚禮的一點一滴，希望為自己留下美好回億。不過，該攝影師拍攝的逾千相片中，有3分1是失焦；大部分更是伴娘的胸部及臀部特寫。夫婦收到該批相片後震怒，2016年入稟成功向攝影師索償，夫婦現時公開經歷，讓他人引以為鑑。<br />\n<br />\n30歲的昂溫和絲特（Paul &amp; Steph Unwin）聘請基爾科西（David Kilcourse）為其婚禮攝影師，但婚禮後他們收到的1636張相片中，有559張是「鬆郁濛」，只有70張拍攝絲特，而拍攝昂溫的竟只得11張；近100張相片都是伴娘才是主角，部分更是胸、臀特寫。<br />\n<br />\n絲特怒斥：「我們錯失了許多婚禮時光，基爾科西甚至沒有影我老爺奶奶的相，亦只有一張相有我父母。」絲特指，基爾科西用奇怪角度拍攝，鏡頭有時根本不能完好地拍攝她和昂溫。<br />\n<br />\n絲特透露，他們除了聘請基爾科西為攝影師，更向他購買攝影套餐，但他沒有按交易提供相簿等物品，在婚禮當日亦是最遲到場。夫婦二人於2016年入稟索償，基爾科西反駁指控，堅稱是惡劣天氣影響婚禮，惟法官最終仍判基爾科西需賠償601英鎊（約6580港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180220/bknint-20180220193000239-0220_17011_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180220%2Fbknint-20180220193000239-0220_17011_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=Dd2PdI4h1STjs4ErCtL6atibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=66e3d9ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180220/bknint-20180220193000239-0220_17011_001.html?refer=hn</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180220/photo/bknint-20180220193000239-0220_17011_001_01p.jpg?20180220222928\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180220%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180220193000239-0220_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180220222928&h=ea6c1d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基爾科西拍下伴娘的胸部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180220/photo/bknint-20180220193000239-0220_17011_001_02b.jpg?20180220222928\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180220%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180220193000239-0220_17011_001_02b.jpg%3F20180220222928&h=5e96e1b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部分相片是伴娘臀部特寫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180220/photo/bknint-20180220193000239-0220_17011_001_03b.jpg?20180220222928\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180220%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180220193000239-0220_17011_001_03b.jpg%3F20180220222928&h=dfb38491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只有少量相片有絲特（右），而且拍攝角度奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dcabd2b734ee3d8eff83f09509ea5eb16a5226","tid":567334,"uid":137233,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:34:49.000Z","msg":"加啲美極又一餐"},{"pid":"1889acb352f8f26112d759143de6927ce724d7e0","tid":567334,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:35:27.000Z","msg":"nice ass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36095d7cbf12f9b147e68a73b475aac76349ef8f","tid":567334,"uid":14497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:36:10.000Z","msg":"伴娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f6a43826df2f5670572170bafc9aac30a707c5","tid":567334,"uid":91633,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:47:27.000Z","msg":"咁都敢俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b424f040b360b95bf463b2155b493cb2a2f7d2e","tid":567334,"uid":45368,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:58:53.000Z","msg":"個攝影師平時應該係影慣車展漫畫展啲龍友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c